data.description: This beautiful home sits on almost 2 acres of land. The location is ideal, you're close enough to major shopping, yet far away enough to enjoy the peaceful country living. There is a huge workshop with a mono-rail for your mechanical needs. There is a mobile home in the back of the property being rented for $750/monthly. From the moment you walk in you will for sure be in awe at the amazing condition of this home. The main floor offers an oversized family room, a formal dining room and the kitchen features an island with an additional dining area. There is a half bathroom on the first floor. The primary suite is also located on the first floor and features a jetted garden tub and a free standing shower. the remaining bedrooms are on the second floor and features a jack and jill bathroom. This home offers so much storage indoors and out.
